import React from 'react' import { weatherReport } from '../@types/weatherReport' const WeatherDisplay = (weatherReport: weatherReport) => { if ((weatherReport.weather === null)) { return null } return (
Weather in {weatherReport.name}
{weatherReport.weather![0].description}
{weatherReport.main!.temp} °C
 
feels like {weatherReport.main!.feels_like} °C
wind: {weatherReport.wind!.speed} m/s
) } export default WeatherDisplay
